title: 01/25/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the Conference Title games and the Conor McGregor lost from the weekend. Why didn't the Packers decide to kick a Field Goal late in the game? What's next for Conor McGregor. NBC Sunday Night Football Color Analyst Cris Collinsworth joins to explain what went wrong for Josh Allen yesterday. ESPN's Ariel Helwani tells us what he thinks Conor McGregor's next move will be. And former NFL Safety and ESPN Analyst Ryan Clark calls in to discuss which Tampa player he was most impressed by.
